
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"



00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 43"



00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,160
Dad.



00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,220
Here you are.



00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,560
You know Jin Mi loves me,



00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,960
but you hinder us.



00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,900
Don’t blame me for being ruthless.



00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:30,940
Lin Xiu.



00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:08,700
The real dream.



00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:28,520
Fish Fairy said,



00:04:28,780 --> 00:04:30,960
the Dream Register records the
whereabouts of the Beast of Dreams.



00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,280
If it’s a real dream,



00:04:32,659 --> 00:04:34,520
the Beast of Dreams
should have been to the Qiwu Palace.



00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,210
"Dream Register"



00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:16,320
It’s really Phoenix’s dream.



00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:34,360
Look, the Heart mansion is like a scorpion,



00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:36,500
while the Three Stars mansion



00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,200
is like a hunter drawing a bow.



00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:43,860
Prey and hunter are destined to be enemies.



00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,280
Even if they have connections occasionally,



00:05:47,020 --> 00:05:49,260
they will be separated finally



00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,940
and won’t meet each other again.



00:05:52,340 --> 00:05:53,560
That’s all for today.



00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,500
Brother Yan You,



00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,280
where are you going to take me?



00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,420
Does Brother Run Yu know?



00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:17,180
I have told him.



00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,940
I’ll take you back to the mire.



00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,260
Are you happy?



00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,700
Wonderful.



00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,560
Where are you going?



00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,580
Go back to the place he should go.



00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,840
The place he should go?



00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:41,060
Here is his home.



00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,380
With the strict rules, suspicion and deception here,



00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,380
his nature and innocent heart



00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,340
will vanish.



00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:51,060
Li, come over.



00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,740
Your Highness.



00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,560
Lord Yan You.



00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:01,940
Li should decide



00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,320
where to go himself.



00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,080
OK.



00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:08,560
Make your choice.



00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,940
Brother Yan You,



00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:16,700
I want to stay with Brother Run Yu.



00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:21,060
Come over.



00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,540
Good boy.



00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,340
What a young snob.



00:07:26,260 --> 00:07:26,920
Fine.



00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:29,300
Let me know if you want to go back.



00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,520
I’ll come to pick you up.



00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:31,340
OK?



00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,880
Yan You,



00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:38,060
I have always regarded you as my brother.



00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,900
If you really want to go, I won’t stop you,



00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,200
but you can come here



00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:45,840
at any time.



00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,140
The door to this palace



00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,140
is always open to you.



00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:53,620
I’m not as capable as Fire Immortal.



00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,880
I’m too humble



00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:56,159
to be your brother.



00:07:58,340 --> 00:07:59,240
Sorry,



00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,380
I can’t do that.



00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,980
Li,



00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,700
thank you for staying with me.



00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,820
The day mother left,



00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:24,120
she hid me in the mire of Yunmeng Pond.



00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:25,480
She told me that



00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,520
if she couldn’t come back,



00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,780
I had to listen to you.



00:08:29,900 --> 00:08:31,800
I remember what she said.



00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,179
Mother also asked me



00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:40,380
to take good care of you all my life.



00:08:41,179 --> 00:08:42,760
I won’t forget that, either.



00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,240
In the future,



00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:48,560
we will keep each other company.



00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:51,520
Can I see Brother Yan You



00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:54,260
and play in the mire afterwards?



00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:56,340
Sure.



00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:59,040
Well, go back to have a rest.



00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,140
Yan You has left.



00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,340
Did I really change a lot?



00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:18,280
I have never



00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,960
done anything wrong in my life.



00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,380
Heavenly Empress



00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:24,800
and Xu Feng



00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,900
can act outrageously,



00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:30,960
but I’m denounced



00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,400
and alienated by those close to me



00:09:35,340 --> 00:09:36,620
because I want to seek revenge.



00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:39,020
White clothes with some mud



00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:41,460
are dirtier than black clothes.



00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:43,520
Gossip is a fearful thing.



00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:45,800
Just ignore it.



00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,580
You’re right.



00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:53,480
Destruction pursues the great.



00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,000
I have embarked on this road.



00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:59,180
No matter what others think,



00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:03,120
I can’t go back.



00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:14,500
Night Immortal has made tremendous contribution to



00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,860
pacifying the Bird Family and allotting rice for food relief.



00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,020
Surprisingly,



00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,640
you always keep a low profile,



00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,220
but you can



00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:23,980
undertake the task alone.



00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:27,120
You’re not inferior to Fire Immortal



00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,600
but more meticulous and thoughtful.



00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:31,640
I feel gratified.



00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,520
I’m flattered.



00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:37,680
Supreme Lord Lao has three treasures.



00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,140
The first is love.



00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,400
Second, never be too much.



00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,540
Third, never be the first in the world.



00:10:43,020 --> 00:10:44,780
They have always been my mottos.



00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:48,860
In the past, I didn’t hold an office,
so I didn’t need to do anything.



00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,860
Now it’s my bounden duty,



00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,740
so I spared no effort to finish it.



00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:55,720
I will try my best



00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:58,200
and won’t let you down.



00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,940
Your Majesty,



00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:03,480
Elder Yin Que from the Bird Family
has submitted a memorial.



00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:07,800
He wants to present the 400-kilometer
Taihu Lake to the Heaven Realm



00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:09,400
to show his loyalty.



00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:12,600
Lake Taihu used to belong to the Arowana Family.



00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:16,680
Night Immortal, I want to give it to you



00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,720
as your fief for commendation.



00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:21,580
What do you think?



00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,560
Thank you, Father.



00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:26,660
The Arowana Family was
annihilated thousands of years ago.



00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,760
Past events have faded like a puff of smoke.



00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:33,160
As your eldest son,
I’m obligated to protect our territory.



00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:36,400
All I want is to share your cares and burdens.



00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,460
Lake Taihu is a fairyland.



00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,020
It shouldn’t be occupied by a single family



00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:46,460
or be one’s private property.



00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,180
Not long ago,



00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:50,700
the dethroned empress incited a war in Dongting Lake,



00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,240
plunging the people into misery and suffering.



00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:55,360
After that, Water Immortal died.



00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:58,400
Immortal Jin Mi observes mourning in Floral Realm.



00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:02,000
Dongting Lake hasn’t recovered.



00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:04,380
Father, why not



00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:08,760
relocate the homeless Water Family in Dongting Lake



00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,320
to Taihu Lake out of mercy?



00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,440
OK.



00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:14,220
It’s wise of you.



00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,580
You should learn from him.



00:12:17,660 --> 00:12:21,820
Night Immortal, I give you
full power to take over Taihu Lake ,



00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,620
reconstruct Dongting Lake,



00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,400
and help the Water Family settle down.



00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,060
I won’t let you down.



00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:39,480
The second Prince was
just deprived of the military power,



00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:42,820
but the first Prince is in power now.



00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:45,940
The second Prince was always sharp.



00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,240
The first Prince



00:12:48,700 --> 00:12:50,700
seems to be nice,



00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:54,260
but he works scrupulously



00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,320
and carefully.



00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,700
Moreover, he is scheming.



00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:01,780
I’m out of luck.



00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:05,420
Why do I always meet those
who are hard to get along with?



00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:06,600
But



00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:09,900
the first Prince is generous.



00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:14,180
He didn’t care about



00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:17,740
Taihu Lake at the Empyrean Cloud Palace.



00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,100
It seems that



00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:21,720
he is far-sighted.



00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,120
You have good taste.



00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:29,620
It’s wise of you to follow
the first Prince when he had no power.



00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,480
Kuang Lu,



00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,840
stop reading. Stop it, okay?



00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:37,920
Look at me,



00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:39,120
okay?



00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:42,400
After the birthday banquet of Moon Immortal,



00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:45,180
you never returned to visit me.



00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:47,460
Are you still angry with me?



00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:48,320
Daddy,



00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:51,760
if you mention my marriage in public again,



00:13:51,860 --> 00:13:53,080
I won’t talk to you any more.



00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:55,660
Follow the first Prince



00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,000
when he had no power?



00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,780
It’s harsh.



00:13:59,360 --> 00:13:59,860
Fine.



00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,960
I will keep my mouth shut, okay?



00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:08,370
Why don’t they govern by
doing nothing that goes against nature



00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:10,300
as Heavenly Emperor does?



00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,540
It’s like marriage.



00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:14,640
Girls of different backgrounds



00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:16,920
will be the same after getting married.



00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:19,160
No matter whether one is at court or out of court,



00:14:19,660 --> 00:14:22,460
it’s the same as long as he takes office.



00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:26,480
Daddy, you keep



00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,340
marrying different women.



00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:29,100
Well…



00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,400
You…



00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,220
It’s like human beings.



00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:35,800
The toilets that human beings build
smell good in three days after completion.



00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:38,440
I don’t know what they think.



00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:42,800
The first Prince plays against the rules,



00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,440
while the second Prince



00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:48,660
doesn’t even know what the rules are.



00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:51,740
Both you and Water Immortal are immortals,



00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,420
but you’re



00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,760
dramatically different.



00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:58,140
Water Immortal?



00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,300
Why should I learn from him?



00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,440
I don’t want to die a violent death.



00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:06,420
Fairy Yuan Ji should put you to the Human Realm.



00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:09,400
The official circles and accountant’s office
in Human Realm are the best places for you.



00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,460
Li,



00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,360
this 400-kilomete Taihu Lake is my mother’s homeland.



00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:30,580
Defend it for me, okay?



00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:36,480
But my magic power is too weak to defend it.



00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,420
There is a large area of mire



00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:42,700
at the bottom of the lake.



00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:44,580
Don’t worry.



00:15:44,780 --> 00:15:47,220
I promise I’ll defend it.



00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,580
Turn to me if you need help.



00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:52,060
Yan You will also help you.



00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:56,180
I’m taking my leave.



00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:06,580
Are you satisfied?



00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:08,540
Time reveals a man’s heart.



00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:10,620
Don’t pretend in front of me.



00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,200
Li is your brother.



00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,640
I think you should know



00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,660
his whereabouts and decisions.



00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,360
Your life is beyond reproach.



00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,260
Aren’t you tired?



00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:23,140
It’s better than death.



00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,600
You’re now only second to Heavenly Emperor.



00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:28,220
You rule heavenly generals and have great power.



00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:30,320
The 400-kilometer Taihu Lake is just recovered.



00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:32,420
You are to be congratulated.



00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:35,080
Your mother would sink happily into the nether world.



00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,220
You’ll leave?



00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:42,940
I like to live



00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,080
alone and freely.



00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:46,660
Fine.



00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:49,660
People of different moral convictions cannot get along.



00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:51,960
Hope we can meet again one day.



00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:54,700
See you again.



00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,180
I bring you



00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:07,720
some gadgets today.



00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:10,599
No need.



00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:12,619
I’m so old.



00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:14,240
I don’t need anything.



00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:19,099
Wow.



00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:22,660
Thank you so much.



00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,460
I’ll take it.



00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,560
You always fear the Jade Hare
at the Guanghan Palace



00:17:26,619 --> 00:17:28,560
every time you go to the Heaven Realm.



00:17:28,780 --> 00:17:30,120
If you don’t like it…



00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:33,100
No, I like it very much.



00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:36,040
Do you know what it is?



00:17:36,620 --> 00:17:37,740
Thunder Drum.



00:17:37,820 --> 00:17:39,410
The drums are like thunder,



00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:41,900
enough to expel tigers, leopards, jackals and wolves,



00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,860
let alone a hare.



00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,160
It’s a good thing.



00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:50,280
It’s very nice of you.



00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:58,400
Lian Qiao, Jin Mi said



00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:00,960
you like most the wonders in the world.



00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,920
You must be bored



00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,160
as you always stay here.



00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:06,840
You can divert yourself with this kaleidoscope.



00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:08,460
Thank you, Your Highness.



00:18:10,140 --> 00:18:12,440
My mother won’t worry about my sneaking out.



00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:16,980
Your Highness, will you take a concubine some day?



00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:19,620
How about me?



00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:23,760
Lian Qiao, you should practice magic power at this age.



00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,220
What are you thinking of?



00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:27,100
I have no intention of doing so.



00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:29,120
I have a younger sworn brother.



00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:32,160
He disdains worldly affairs.



00:18:32,360 --> 00:18:34,880
If you don’t mind, I’ll introduce him to you.



00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:36,200
I don’t mind



00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:37,560
if he is half as good as you.



00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,720
I have to go to meet Jin Mi.



00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:48,960
Xuan Ling Lord Doumu



00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:51,360
once wrote a set of flower scriptures
tens of thousands of years ago.



00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:53,160
Unfortunately, they disappeared,



00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:55,320
which made Chief Peony heart-broken.



00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:58,880
Unexpectedly, Night Immortal has great magic power.



00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,320
He found the scriptures



00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,620
and gave them to us.



00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:04,460
Chief Peony



00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:06,000
has never praised anyone



00:19:06,140 --> 00:19:07,560
in these tens of thousands of years.



00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:11,240
Night Immortal doesn’t do anything purposely,



00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:13,160
but he can solve everything satisfactorily



00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:15,420
and inadvertently.



00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:17,740
He can lift a finger



00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:19,440
to solve all difficult things.



00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,380
Those who he helps



00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:23,280
won’t think they owe him.



00:19:24,300 --> 00:19:27,620
Silent and soft, it moistens everything.



00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:32,500
It’s the most difficult to do thing by the light of nature.



