Mi.



00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,200
Fish Fairy.



00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:01,620
Don’t worry.



00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:06,700
I’m dealing with the work of Water Immortal for you.



00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:08,880
Observe mourning for your father without worry here.



