if, I mean if,



00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:43,520
the murderer



00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:45,400
is an immortal here,



00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:50,060
will Heavenly Emperor handle it impartially?



00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,740
Why do you have such a question?



00:20:53,820 --> 00:20:55,260
It has been a long time,



00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:58,440
but there is no any clue.



00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:00,780
The murderer must have an eminent identity,



00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:05,580
or Heavenly Emperor would have investigated it.



00:21:06,660 --> 00:21:07,700
Perhaps Heavenly Emperor



00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,560
doesn’t want to impeach him.



00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:22,380
The Law Enforcement Hall
reported the clues several times.



00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:24,500
