00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,620
my father mentions nothing about it



00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:28,660
and tightly blocks the passage of message.



00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:30,420
I don’t have any evidence,



00:21:30,710 --> 00:21:31,960
so I can’t make presumptuous guesses.



00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,980
Who do you suspect?



00:21:38,600 --> 00:21:39,980
I just don’t understand.



00:21:40,380 --> 00:21:43,850
My father didn’t seek fame and wealth



00:21:43,850 --> 00:21:45,200
and held himself aloof from the world all his life.



00:21:46,220 --> 00:21:47,960
Why was he killed?



00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:50,400
Why?



00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,480
Maybe it’s because of me.



00:21:54,260 --> 00:21:55,900
Originally,



00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:59,840
we were engaged



00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:01,300
because we loved each other,



00:22:02,180 --> 00:22:03,440
but



00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,990
I, the poorest and weakest idle immortal



00:22:05,990 --> 00:22:06,960
in the Heaven Realm,



00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,840
gained the support of



00:22:10,340 --> 00:22:12,680
Water Immortal, Wind Immortal



00:22:13,360 --> 00:22:14,700
and even the Floral Realm overnight.



00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:18,520
Others think I want to
rebel and fight for the throne.



00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:24,280
Dad.



00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:31,740
Mi, don’t worry.



00:22:32,540 --> 00:22:34,360
I won’t let Water Immortal



00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:36,480
die distressingly.



00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:46,600
Mu Ci, I own your life now.



00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,360
Go back to recuperate this time.



00:22:48,780 --> 00:22:50,100
Don’t sneak out.



00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:51,020
OK.



00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:52,080
Don’t cheat me.



00:22:52,280 --> 00:22:53,380
When did I cheat you?



00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,760
You always cheat me.



00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:58,340
Let’s live here today.



00:22:58,420 --> 00:22:58,920
OK.



