Hu.



00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,220
Coming.



00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:16,440
Lead them to their room.



00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,520
You go upstairs first.
I’ll go to check what happens.



00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:18,780
Dear customers, please follow me.



