Demon Lord comes. Get out of the way.



00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,420
Leave.



00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,780
You!



00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:29,370
Are you blind?



00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:31,450
How dare you block the way of King of Yan City?



00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,320
Your Highness.



00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:36,680
I was wondering who swaggered before others.



00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:37,960
It turns out to be you.



00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,140
When did the guard of Bian City



00:23:43,300 --> 00:23:45,480
become the pawn of Demon Lord?



00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,940
I’m on my way



00:23:48,060 --> 00:23:49,260
to the city gate



00:23:49,300 --> 00:23:51,160
to invite King of Gu City and Demon Lord
by order of King of Bian City.



00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:52,580
King of Bian City holds a banquet tonight.



00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:53,900
He wants to make things right



00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:55,560
with King of Gu City in front of Demon Lord.



00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,860
