00:24:19,140 --> 00:24:19,920
Yes.



00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,480
Why don’t you



00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:22,360
bring Princess Liu Ying back?



00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:24,080
It’s a great merit.



00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:27,240
The banquet is the first priority now.



00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,840
If we push her too far,



00:24:30,020 --> 00:24:31,320
we’ll alert her.



00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:35,740
I won’t fear her after the success of the banquet.



00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:37,540
Keep watch on her.



00:24:37,620 --> 00:24:38,260
