00:24:43,740 --> 00:24:44,560
to stay away from trouble.



00:24:46,280 --> 00:24:48,620
In this case, you should go back



00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,500
to help.



00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:52,960
No. What if you escape again?



00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,300
Moreover,



00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,160
Demon Lord and King of Gu City don’t like me.



00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:58,140
I don’t want to go back to upset them.



00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,410
I feel free here,



00:24:59,660 --> 00:25:01,080
and it’s convenient to ask for information.



00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:04,140
Over the years,



00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:08,160
I know very well that I have done a lot of wrong things,



00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:12,400
but now, every time I think of you…



00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:14,600
What do you think of me?



00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,470
Every time I think of you,



00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:19,930
I will tell myself that



00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:21,860
I can’t let you down again.



00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:28,200
A fault confessed is half redressed.



00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:30,680
Don’t mention the past.



00:25:31,300 --> 00:25:32,740
After the banquet,



00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:35,420
let’s go to visit my father



00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:36,900
and ask him to preside over our wedding ceremony.



00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:40,800
OK.



00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:19,080
Cheers.



00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:20,160
Please.



00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:34,060
Why don’t I see Princess Liu Ying today?



00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:36,100
She is a wild girl.



00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:37,820
She has been out for long.



00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:42,980
She has much enjoyment in Heaven Realm
and forgets to go back home.



00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:48,220
You’re kidding.



00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:49,840
Liu Ying is stubborn and disobedient,



00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:52,020
but she discerns the cardinal principles.



00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:55,700
She has political integrity.



00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,540
I heard that Princess Liu Ying



00:26:59,060 --> 00:27:01,320
is close to Fire Immortal.



00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:05,360
There are a lot of unfounded rumors.



00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:10,500
A few days ago, Liu Ying was chased by her family.



00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:13,680
She hid outside and didn’t even dare to go back.



00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:15,580
What do you mean?



00:27:15,620 --> 00:27:17,940
You’re well-informed.



00:27:18,980 --> 00:27:21,120
You should know what I mean.



00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,180
Stop that.



00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,740
You’re my capable assistants.



00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:30,240
Here’s to our Demon Realm.



00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,520
From now on,



00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:35,200
write off all our old scores.



00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:36,940
Demon Lord, please.



00:27:37,060 --> 00:27:37,540
Please.



00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:39,160
King of Gu City, please.



00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:40,380
Please.



00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:58,260
Good dance.



00:27:58,300 --> 00:28:03,040
I propose to drink a toast to the host, King of Bian City.



00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:07,860
To King of Bian City.



00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:15,240
Today, Demon Lord, King of Gu City



00:28:15,660 --> 00:28:18,580
and other kings come from afar.



00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:21,820
My humble house is honored by your presence.



00:28:22,180 --> 00:28:24,820
Return after thoroughly enjoying yourselves.



00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,900
I empty my glass first to show my respect to you.



00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:27,610
Come.



00:28:28,320 --> 00:28:28,900
Cheers.



00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,920
Your Highness, bad news.



00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:56,960
Demon Lord



00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:58,180
is dead.



00:28:59,020 --> 00:28:59,880
What?



00:29:09,820 --> 00:29:11,540
Demon Lord…



00:29:11,580 --> 00:29:13,720
Demon Lord…



00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:22,520
Guards, take him!



00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:36,140
The doctor diagnosed that
Demon Lord was poisoned and died.



00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:38,400
King of Gu City has imprisoned all our people.



00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:39,680
He said they would be beheaded



00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:40,930
as there were human testimony and material evidence.



00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:43,400
What do others think of such a big thing?



00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:45,200
Have you informed Elder Wang of Qing City?



00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:47,220
Demon Lord thinks highly of King of Gu City.



00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:49,140
He has half of the military and political power.



00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,880
With the evidence, what can they do?



00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,520
I have no time to explain, Your Highness,



00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:54,840
let’s rush to the demon prison.



00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:57,220
I’ll fight desperately to help you save your father.



00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:58,260
OK.



00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,540
Your Highness, what’s wrong?



00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:23,380
It’s late.



00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:26,540
You said that my family was imprisoned.



00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,420
You’re my father’s trusted follower,



00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:31,940
and you greeted the sedan chair of
King of Yan City for my father yesterday.



00:30:32,380 --> 00:30:34,620
Why didn’t King of Gu City capture you?



00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:35,960
I,



00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:38,720
I fought desperately my way out.



00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,920
Really?



00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,800
As you said,



00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:55,200
you should be wanted by King of Gu City everywhere.



00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:57,740
How can you come here quietly?



00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,920
You must have deployed your men outside the prison.



00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,120
As long as I break into the prison and rescue my father,



00:31:01,140 --> 00:31:02,760
he will be declared guilty.



00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:05,240
It’s not the time to show your cleverness.



00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,480
If you really go to the demon prison with me,



00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:09,460
you can reunite with your father



00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:11,740
and won’t suffer much.



00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,500
You’re completely without conscience.



00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:18,980
You collude with King of Gu City



00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:20,320
to frame my father up.



00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:22,880
Now you want to capture me to receive a reward?



00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:25,820
King of Bian City colluded with his daughter
to plot against Demon Lord.



00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:26,700
She refuses to be captured.



00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:27,740
Take her.



00:32:03,300 --> 00:32:04,140
Go.



00:32:16,770 --> 00:32:17,410
You want to go?



00:32:17,850 --> 00:32:18,620
It’s not that easy.



00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:24,400
Fight.



00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:32,520
Mu Ci, now King of Yan City is dead,



00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:34,600
and King of Bian City has been imprisoned.



00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,880
King of Gu City has ruled Demon Realm.



00:32:37,260 --> 00:32:39,520
You can’t save your former master
even if you pose as a hero here.



00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:42,460
You’d better run for your life.



00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:43,980
Get help to save your father.



00:32:43,980 --> 00:32:45,960
No. I can’t leave you behind.



00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:47,150
Don’t worry.



00:32:47,670 --> 00:32:49,440
I can defeat them.



00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:51,760
Be careful.



00:32:58,240 --> 00:33:00,280
Why are you in a fret today?



00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:02,120
I met my mother.



00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:04,020
Did Heavenly Empress



00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:06,860
really kill Water Immortal and Wind Immortal?



00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,820
She didn’t deny it,



00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:12,480
so she must be involved.



00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:15,720
Sorry, I can’t share your cares and burdens.



00:33:16,940 --> 00:33:17,960
I gain nothing until now.



00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:22,240
I didn’t kill them, but they died because of me.



00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:25,340
My mother killed them



00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:28,160
because of me.



00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:33,560
If my mother really killed Water Immortal,



00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:36,140
she will die.



00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:40,260
By then,



00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:43,540
how can I save mother



00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,600
and explain to Jin Mi?



00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:53,380
It must weigh upon my conscience.



00:33:54,360 --> 00:33:55,460
It’s really difficult.



00:33:58,820 --> 00:34:00,960
Your Highness, something wrong
happened in Demon Realm.



00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,460
I wasn’t at home,



00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,880
so I just know these things.



00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:07,400
King of Gu City used this treacherous plot



00:34:07,420 --> 00:34:08,600
to lure me to the prison to save my father



00:34:08,620 --> 00:34:09,940
and declare my father guilty.



00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,679
My father pacified Demon Realm



00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:13,100
when the six realms were in a mess.



00:34:13,179 --> 00:34:14,600
If he is put to death rashly,



00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:16,800
the murderer will remain at large.



00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:19,159
Your Majesty, please help him.



00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:21,280
Princess of Bian City, as you said,



00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:24,600
King of Yan City was poisoned and died



00:34:24,659 --> 00:34:26,020
at the banquet in your home.



00:34:26,219 --> 00:34:28,139
And the doctor has made a diagnosis.



00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:30,280
Do you have evidence to prove that



00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,420
King of Gu City frame your father up?



00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:35,739
I saw my father’s general turned traitor.



00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,340
He had a guilty conscience,



00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:38,620
or he wouldn’t do that.



00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,050
I am hurt.



00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,719
Your Majesty, please investigate it.



00:34:42,199 --> 00:34:44,179
If King of Bian City really poisoned King of Yan City,



00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:47,520
it’s understandable that his subordinate turned traitor.



00:34:47,699 --> 00:34:49,620
My father has a good reputation in Demon Realm.



00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:51,230
He always tried to fix the relationship



00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:52,679
between Heaven Realm and Demon Realm.



00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:56,100
Don’t you trust my father?



00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,780
Princess Liu Ying, calm down.



00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,940
How can I calm myself down?



00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:03,680
We are on friendly terms with Heaven Realm.



00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,340
My father is framed by King of Gu City



00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,140
and will be put to death soon.



00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,800
I came from afar to ask you for help,



00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:11,160
but you sit by idly and remain indifferent.



00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,860
You’re cold-blooded.



00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:18,580
I listened to your story as you got hurt



00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,340
and your father was wronged.



00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:22,560
All immortals are here.



00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:24,460
King of Bian City is wronged without evidence,



00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:26,360
how I can have a hand in Demon Realm's affairs



00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,720
thousands of kilometers away?



00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,700
King of Yan City died.



00:35:32,140 --> 00:35:34,560
Demon Realm is chaotic without a leader.



00:35:35,120 --> 00:35:37,720
We can have a hand in it.



00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:41,560
After this accident, Princess Liu Ying is hurt.



00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:43,500
You must be exhausted.



00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:46,520
Immortal Tai Si,



00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:48,020
take her to the side hall for treatment.



00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:50,980
Yes.



00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:55,580
Princess.



00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:56,940
Princess, wait for me.



00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,160
Her family



00:35:58,220 --> 00:35:59,380
is on friendly terms with us,



00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:01,860
or I would punish her for being rude.



00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,320
Princess.



00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,480
Princess, wait for me.



00:36:09,860 --> 00:36:10,820
Princess, wait for me.



00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:13,020
Princess, wait for me.



00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,160
No one in this vast realm



00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:17,480
speaks for my family.



00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:20,640
Immortals are disappointing.



00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,740
Be patient.



00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:26,040
The first Prince is trying to persuade His Majesty.



00:36:26,260 --> 00:36:28,580
Take it easy.



00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:31,820
I’d better rely on myself.



00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:43,700
Father, you’re large-minded.



00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:47,640
Princess Liu Ying wants to save her father.



00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:49,120
Although it’s something that we shouldn’t do,



00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:53,300
we can still intervene in it.



00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:54,960
If we leave them alone,



00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,460
the three kings in Demon Realm



00:36:57,640 --> 00:37:00,340
won’t be able to restrain each other.



00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:01,940
We have to guard against it.



00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:05,720
Among the kings in Demon Realm,



00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:08,920
the Great Elder, King of Qing City
lives in seclusion for cultivation



00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,160
and ignores all things.



00:37:10,740 --> 00:37:12,740
King of Gu City was overweeningly ambitious.



00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,900
He hides behind King of Yan City



00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:17,440
and has been stirring up trouble over the years.



00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:19,640
Obviously, he wants to rebel.



00:37:20,180 --> 00:37:23,380
Luckily, King of Bian City restrains them,



00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,120
so Demon Realm is at peace.



00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,280
Without King of Bian City,



00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,620
other elders



00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:30,640
may be ambitious



00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:33,120
or trim their sails to the wind.



00:37:33,580 --> 00:37:36,160
The six realms may witness havoc again.



00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:38,600
Moreover, this case has many doubtful points.



00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:41,300
It can’t be closed hastily.



00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:43,840
We should send some people to investigate it.



00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:45,740
Your Majesty,



00:37:45,940 --> 00:37:49,840
Night Immortal and Moon Immortal are right.



00:37:49,980 --> 00:37:53,520
It’s difficult to maintain Demon Realm at peace,



00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,920
so King of Gu City



00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:58,580
can’t be the only strong one.



00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:02,960
Who can take this task?



00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:08,700
I’m willing to go to Demon Realm
to share your cares and burdens.



00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:11,360
Fire Immortal



00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:13,080
knows the things in Demon Realm best.



00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,680
How long has he been grounded
to reflect on his misdeeds?



00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,180
It has been a full month.



00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,620
Why don’t you kneel down?



00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,500
I’m innocent.



00:38:52,790 --> 00:38:53,630
Why should I kneel?



00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:26,600
King of Gu City, why do you want to kill me hastily?



00:39:26,820 --> 00:39:28,400
Do you have a guilty conscience?



00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:34,380
King of Bian City, given our old friendship,



00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:36,180
I address you as King of Bian City.



00:39:36,780 --> 00:39:38,560
Demon Lord was kind to you,



00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:40,720
but you returned kindness with ingratitude,



00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:43,020
poisoned Demon Lord and usurped the throne.



00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:45,520
The evidence is certain.



00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:48,340
Your crime deserves more than death.



00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,760
You’re slinging mud at me.



00:39:49,900 --> 00:39:51,420
Since I entertained Demon Lord,



00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:53,700
I wouldn’t poison him at my place.



00:39:53,860 --> 00:39:56,280
You frame me up deliberately. You…



00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:04,960
I’ll kill you for the sake of Demon Realm



00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:09,320
and offer your blood as a sacrifice to Demon Lord.



00:40:10,340 --> 00:40:13,620
It’s a good time now.



00:40:13,620 --> 00:40:16,360
I’ll kill you in person.



00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,060
Well,



00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:21,120
I know you love Liu Ying dearly.



00:40:21,700 --> 00:40:24,340
I promise I’ll send her to Wangchuan River



00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:28,980
to be reunited with you after I capture her.



00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,560
You bastard.



00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:32,620
Bastard.



00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:36,720
It’s the time.



00:40:36,930 --> 00:40:37,930
Take the Demon Dagger.



00:40:49,620 --> 00:40:51,040
The end of natural law,



00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,580
the convene of sun and moon.



00:40:53,400 --> 00:40:54,840
To come and to go



00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,700
are obscure and subtle.



00:40:58,180 --> 00:41:00,960
All the beasts and demons...



00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:14,360
Who dares to hurt my father?



00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:17,060
Liu Ying,



00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:19,860
here you are.



00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,980
Take her.



00:41:43,200 --> 00:41:44,700
I was wondering who you were.



00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:47,300
It turns out to be the surviving supporter
of the Spirit-Vanishing Family.



00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:51,800
I’ll annihilate you all today.


